Adventurer: Changed the card to reveal and add 3 treasure cards to the player's hand rather than 2.

Mine: Changed toFlag variable passed tor gainCard call within the playMine() function from 2 to 1, causing the card to move a new card to the player's deck instead of their hand

Smithy: Changed the card to draw 4 cards instead of 3.

Village: changed trash flag for the discardCard call from 0 to 1, causing the discard to remove the card from the game rather than adding it to the "played" pile.
